Ranger Help for: train animal
===============================

SYNTAX:      train <follower> <trick>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to teach their bonded animal follower a new
trick. The available tricks are: power, speed, senses, dart, unleash,
fetch, deliver, and seek. Not all followers can learn all tricks, as
some require a certain level of intelligence. The smarter the follower,
the more tricks it can learn. Training takes time and patience, and
the chance of success depends on the Ranger's charisma and the
follower's intelligence.
